# ===================================================================
# CONFIGURATIE STAPPEN:
# ===================================================================
# 
# 1. Azure App Registration:
#    - Ga naar: https://portal.azure.com
#    - App registrations → New registration
#    - Naam: "Inspiration Point Booking System"
#    - Kopieer Client ID en Tenant ID hierboven
#
# 2. Client Secret:
#    - Ga naar: Certificates & secrets → New client secret
#    - Kopieer de SECRET VALUE (niet de ID!) hierboven
#
# 3. API Permissions:
#    - Ga naar: API permissions → Add a permission
#    - Microsoft Graph → Application permissions
#    - Selecteer: Mail.Send (b633e1c5-b582-4048-a93e-9f11b44c7e96)
#    - BELANGRIJK: Grant admin consent!
#
# 4. Email Account:
#    - Zorg dat noreply@inspirationpoint.nl bestaat in je Office 365
#    - Account moet Exchange Online licentie hebben
#    - Test met microsoftGraphEmailService.sendTestEmail()
#
# ===================================================================

